<DocsPageSection>
    <DocsPageSectionHeader Title="Batch Edit">
        <Paragraph>
            The grid can be set to batch edit mode by setting <Code>BatchEdit</Code> to true. This allows the user to edit multiple rows and then save all the changes at once.
        </Paragraph>
